These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-7-1::.
3 different games are played: monopoly, snooker, poker
House: wooden, tower, ranch-style
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, aconite, bellflower
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, fuchsia, mauve
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, ritmeester, cain
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, subway, scooter
 1. the person who likes ebony is not the person who growsaconite##6
 2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 3. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the left of the person who likes mauve##5
 4. the cain-smoker is somewhere between the person playing monopoly and the person driving the scooter##7
 5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
 6. the person playing snooker is the person driving the boat##1
 7. the person who growsbellflower is not the ritmeester-smoker##6
 8. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the tower house##1
 9. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
10. the person driving the scooter is not the person who growsbellflower##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3     |
| Game      | monopoly       | snooker  | poker     |
| House          | ranch-style       | tower  | wooden    |
| Flower         | orchid  | bellflower   | aconite |
| Color   | ebony | mauve   | fuchsia     |
| Cigar   | tiparillo  | cain | ritmeester   |
| Transport           | subway  | boat      | scooter  |

