4. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the fan r&b##5
5. the person who likes coral is not the person who's birthday is in january##6
6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3
7. the person who likes ivory is the fan r&b##1
8. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere between the snookerrot-smoker and the person who's sport is weightlifting##7
9. the fan folk is somewhere to the right of the snookerrot-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |      3      |
| Sport      | sailing       | badminton      | weightlifting    |
| Cigar          | snookerrot     | cain        | tiparillo        |
| Music-Genre           | house  | r&b | folk   |
| Birthday   | april | january           | september |
| Color   | aquamarine  | ivory    | coral   |
| Game     | chess        | billiard          | snooker         |

