 1. the person who's birthday is in march is not the aristoff-smoker##6
 2. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking sprite##7
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is the person traveling to marseilles##1
 5. the aristoff-smoker is the person traveling to marseilles##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4
 7. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 8. the cottage house is the person who likes light-blue##1
 9. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the right of the colonial house##5
10. the person drinking almond-milk is the person traveling to venice##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5

